740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01585">Andreas-Salomé an Schnitzler, 19. 2. 1906</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01587">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 6. 3. 1906</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01582">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, [zwischen
